{"tid":936784,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[打手post] ikea 個雪糕真心掂","createTime":"2018-12-11T04:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T10:56:38.000Z","uid":87687,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc2ded230af2f2f6aba3d462588cc6590b76c5d","tid":936784,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/11/123806_4c6f4cfded0226b0dd657774e19b31e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F11%2F123806_4c6f4cfded0226b0dd657774e19b31e9.jpg&h=62bbb9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豆腐味，我知呢個味係好僻好少人屌，但真心ok. 小弟幾十年雲呢拿支持者都係咁話。以前返工會食到豆腐味雪糕杯，但後來好少食到了。平時一見到有豆腐味就會狗衝的。<br />\n<br />\n佢今次有個小twist, 就係有黃糖碎，所以應該叫豆花味？幾蚊雞，抵屌。<br />\n<br />\n利申：豆腐，雲呢拿，紅豆是top3. <br />\n<br />\n廷申閱讀：為甚麼ikea的食物平靚正？原來。。。<br />\n<br />\n自已google. <br />\n<br />\nspoiler :係心理學trick，今你覺得佢既傢俬都好似佢d小食咁平靚正。"},{"pid":"15cf9a7809da04c5a02f0e45f49ef20a5b1cc307","tid":936784,"uid":21423,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04d5fbaacb91d3142e62219bd923dc0a94508f1e","tid":936784,"uid":177955,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"15cf9a7809da04c5a02f0e45f49ef20a5b1cc307","tid":936784,"uid":21423,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpQef94.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpQef94.gif&h=0443d472&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb71c571d55fdc328eb20108dd31fcf31946b8ff","tid":936784,"uid":13831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:58:44.000Z","msg":"的確係豆腐花味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add91c8ff158134d430177e2e367cdba305ba398","tid":936784,"uid":176834,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"re